<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528085422598.png" alt="image-20210528085422598" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>3.点击下一步</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://superdong.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/image-20210528085449857.png" alt="image-20210528085449857" loading="lazy"></figure>
